# A son of [[Israel]], i.e., a descendant of the [[patriarch]] [[Jacob]].
# The tribe descended from Judah, from which David and his lineage came from.
# The name of the southern kingdom which continued to be ruled by the Davidic dynasty after Solomon's death and the breakup of the united monarchy, with the northern portion keeping the name Israel. 

